  <h2>Tech Needs to Focus on Ethics</h2>
    <p>This is a paragraph about ethical technology.</p>
  <h3>Tech Companies are Selectively Ethical</h3>
    <p>I'm not someone who thinks that all businesses are inherently evil, or that tech companies are run by evil robots.</p>
  <h2>Why Regulating Tech Companies Is So Difficult</h2>
    <p>The people in charge of regulating these companies have very little understanding of the actual functionality of these companies' products. The world of politics is always behind the world of tech, and any regulations will be outdated in just a few years.</p>
